    <desc>Delete an alarm when it is no longer necessary.</desc>
  </info>

  <title>Remove an alarm</title>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Press the <gui style="button">Alarm</gui> button.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Press the button with a tick mark on the top right corner.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Select the alarms you wish to delete from the list.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Press <gui style="button">Delete</gui>.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

  <note style="tip">
    <p>Alternately, you can right click on an alarm, to bring up the delete button.</p>
  </note>

